criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. diagnosis of systemic AL amyloidosis;

          2. treatment-naïve (pre-treatment data collected at participating center available for
             retrospective part);

          3. age ≥18 years;

          4. ability to understand and willingness to sign an informed consent (patients who
             already sign informed consent for clinical data to be used in retrospective analyses
             will be accepted);

          5. planned (or ongoing) follow-up at participating center.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. non-AL amyloidosis;

          2. previous treatment for AL amyloidosis.
